呢排hit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過樓主咁有心係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客氣喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實傳媒應該去做教育，而家就多得新假期呢啲加個icon上去教人呃like，講邊度死邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b11963537444888ec6d26bbc261ec4509fa379","tid":299012,"uid":172705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:01:21.000Z","msg":"星期日都比入架可？"}]}